<p>&nbsp;Headquartered at 20/F, CITIC Tower, 1 Tim Mei Avenue, Admiralty, Hong Kong, Millennia Capital Partners Limited continues to position itself as a trusted provider of customized financing and investment solutions. By combining industry expertise, flexible lending structures, and personalized client service, the firm helps businesses and investors unlock capital, improve liquidity, and pursue long-term financial growth while maintaining ownership of their valuable investment assets.</p>
